      • fileBug

        @SSCRequiredActionsPermitted(value="POST=/api/v\\d+/projectVersions/\\d+/issues/action")
public JSONMap fileBug(String applicationVersionId,
                                                                                                                Map<String,Object> issueDetails,
                                                                                                                List<String> issueInstanceIds)
        File a bug via an SSC native bug tracker integration. Before calling this method, the authenticateForBugFiling(String, String, String) must have been called (if isBugTrackerAuthenticationRequired(String) returns true).
        Parameters:
        applicationVersionId - for which to submit a bug
        issueDetails - for the bug to be submitted
        issueInstanceIds - for which to submit the bug
        Returns:
        JSONMap containing SSC response data
